Title: Tyler Perry's Meet The Browns: Season 5

reviewText: I couldn't wait to see what funny antics Mr. Brown would get into each week, it's a shame that this show was cancelled. With the stuff that is on television these days, it was great to tune in and get laughs from Mr. Brown, family, and friends. Glad that amazon made it possible to relive these funny moments.
Title: Tyler Perry's Meet The Browns: Season 5
